Start a timer.

Params:
	func = The function to call when the timer expires.
	duration = Timer duration.
	isRepeat = Whether to repeat the timer.

Example:
---
listener.timer({
	writeln("3 seconds!");
},dur!"msecs"(3000),true);
---

